First Department,

June, 1956

(June 1, 1956) In the Matter of Moses Kooperstein et al., Appellants, against James M. Power et al., Constituting the Board of Elections of the City of New York, Respondents.

Order appealed from affirmed. No opinion. Concur — Peek, P. J., Breitel, Botein and Rabin, JJ.
